OL,3,CGaza documentary breached BBC
OL,4,Ceditorial guidelines of accuracy,
OL,5,Creview finds
OL,7,FThe programme 'Gaza: How To Survive A
OL,8,FWarzone' aired in February but was
OL,9,Flater pulled by the BBC after it
OL,10,Femerged the 13-year-old who narrated
OL,11,Fthe documentary, Abdullah, is the son
OL,12,Fof Ayman Alyazouri, who has worked as
OL,13,FHamas's deputy minister of agriculture.
OL,15,FThe review, led by Peter Johnston who
OL,16,Fis the director of editorial
OL,17,Fcomplaints and reviews, was set up to
OL,18,Fdetermine whether editorial guidelines
OL,19,Fwere broken and whether any
OL,20,Fdisciplinary action is needed.
