OL,3,CGaza documentary breached BBC
OL,4,Ceditorial guidelines of accuracy,
OL,5,Creview finds
OL,7,FIt found the BBC breached its
OL,8,Feditorial guidelines on accuracy by
OL,9,F"failing to disclose information about
OL,10,Fthe child narrator's father's position
OL,11,Fwithin the Hamas-run government".
OL,13,FBBC Director-General Tim Davie has
OL,14,Fsince apologised following the review
OL,15,Ffindings.
OL,17,FHe said: "Peter Johnston's report
OL,18,Fidentifies a significant failing in
OL,19,Frelation to accuracy in this
OL,20,Fdocumentary.
