OL,3,CGaza documentary breached BBC
OL,4,Ceditorial guidelines of accuracy,
OL,5,Creview finds
OL,7,FThe report found nobody at the BBC
OL,8,Fknew of the father's position when the
OL,9,Fdocumentary first aired on February
OL,10,F17, but that three people at Hoyo
OL,11,FFilms, the independent production
OL,12,Fcompany which produced the film, were
OL,13,Faware.
OL,15,FIt added the report did not find the
OL,16,Fproduction company intentionally
OL,17,Fmisled the corporation, but does find
OL,18,Fthe firm bears most of the
OL,19,Fresponsibility for the failure.
